snippet.description: Homer Bailey doesn't even need to be at his best to win at Wrigley Field.

snippet.title: Vettel asked to make way for teammate again
snippet.description: Four-time world champion Sebastian Vettel isn't used to being asked to step aside for a teammate. Now it's happened twice in two races.

snippet.title: Prizefighter Rubin 'Hurricane' Carter dies at 76
snippet.description: Rubin "Hurricane" Carter never surrendered hope of regaining his freedom, not even after he was convicted of a triple murder, then convicted again and abandoned by many prominent supporters.

snippet.title: More bodies from ship; transcript reveals wavering
snippet.description: Divers continued the grim work of recovering bodies from inside a sunken South Korean ferry Monday, securing a new entryway into the wreck, as a newly released transcript showed the ship was crippled by confusion and indecision well after it began listing. The transcript suggests that the chaos may have added to a death toll that could eventually exceed 300.

snippet.title: Seafood study: Up to 32 percent imported to U.S. is caught illegally
